The worldwide Challenge Cup competition allows the most promising startups to win prizes, make connections, and share their vision on a global stage. This year, 1776 is partnering with 75 cities to host Challenge Cup Local events. One winner will advance with a free trip to the Global Finals at Challenge Festival in New York City from 13-17 November 2017. There, the finalists will compete for the grand prizes as well as spend time with the investors, customers, media, and other key connections that can help them succeed on a global scale. Want your startup to compete in Challenge Cup Lagos? Apply today.